meetings.coach_feedback: Facilitation: tight. Ownership clear. You interrupted 1 time(s); pause 2–3s after questions. Good structure; tighten decision framing earlier with explicit options.

discussion_points: Installer packaging/signing: MSIX vs MSI tradeoffs.
UI parity gaps: Preferences, onboarding tooltips, system tray menu.
Perf regressions on Win11 23H2: +400ms cold start.
decisions: Commit to MSIX for beta; MSI fallback for enterprise pilots.
De-scope advanced theming; keep light/dark only.
open_issues: Code-signing cert automation unreliable in CI.
Tray icon flicker on multi-monitor setups; repro needed.
next_steps: Finalize MSIX pipeline in CI; QA smoke test signed build.
Design to provide final Preferences assets.

informational: Read packaging decision doc: MSIX vs MSI.
Review startup time trends in perf dashboard.
Check CI logs for code signing failures.
reflective: Beta scope still wide; nominate one more cut candidate.
Tray init may cause both perf issues; try simplified boot path.
